Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:07.26,special,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(468,321)}納˙托庫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圖斯克爾南方的納˙托庫
